				<td colspan="2"><span>Some stack, some don't<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
I'm not at the level that I can get all these things you mention, so don't take this as definite, but here's my understanding:
<br />

<br />
In general, instrument modifiers do NOT stack. Examples would be standard instruments, epic, LDoN instrument augs and puretone (I think, as puretone just gives you a fixed modifier for all instruments).
<br />

<br />
Other effects such as amp, IM/SM skills and VotS (its a clicky remember) will stack, up to your modifier cap (which can be expanded with AA)
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
